Class Area

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.csupomona.cs.cs141.FinalProject.Area

  • public class Area
extends Object
    This class represents a space on the map. The Area can hold an Item, a person, or both. It will also be able to return what is inside of it.
    Author:
    Team Jedi
